<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span> صحيح ـ <span class="c2">((الصحيحة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٣٥٢٣)</span>: ق.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>